                                     Table "public.reported_accounts"
        Column         |            Type             | Collation | Nullable |           Default           
-----------------------+-----------------------------+-----------+----------+-----------------------------
 reported_account_id   | uuid                        |           | not null | 
 account_no            | character varying(20)       |           | not null | 
 bank_code             | character varying(10)       |           | not null | 
 linked_customer_cif   | character varying(20)       |           |          | 
 valid_report_count    | integer                     |           |          | 0
 unique_reporter_count | integer                     |           |          | 0
 total_reported_amount | bigint                      |           |          | 0
